<concept id="zoomfactor" xml:lang="en-US">
   <title id="title__Toc50995858">ZOOMFACTOR System Variable</title>
   <conbody>
      <section><title>Zoom factor</title><p>Specifies the incremental change in zoom with each mouse-wheel action, whether forward or backward. When zooming in, the incremental step decreases gradually allowing to focus on a particularly detail easily. Values between 3 and 100 are accepted. The higher the number, the more the change.</p><p><table id="table_r32_ncz_hnb">
               <tgroup cols="2">
                  <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*" />
                  <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3*" />
                  <tbody>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/type" />
                        <entry><p conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/short" /></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/saved_in" />
                        <entry><p conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/registry" /></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/range" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>3 to 100</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/default_value" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>40</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table></p></section>
   </conbody>
</concept>
